Air Quality mobile app
How to use:
By default, the app fetchs Air information of the current deviceâ€™s location.
You can pick anywhere you want by clicking on the top-left button, a Google map screen will appear, then scroll/swipe the map to the location you want to know the Air Quality. Finally click the blue bottom-right button to go to the Detail info screen.
Permission:
Location permission: this app needs the location permission in order to get lat/lon of your current location, than fetch Air quality of your location.
